# Transpersonal NPC Blueprint
# Base blueprint class for all transpersonal NPCs with consciousness-based behavior

Class: BP_TranspersonalNPC
Parent: Character

Components:
- NPCBehaviorComponent (UNPCBehaviorComponent)
- ConsciousnessVisualization (UStaticMeshComponent)
- EmotionalAura (UParticleSystemComponent)
- DialogueComponent (UDialogueComponent)

Variables:
- NPCArchetype (ENPCArchetype): ShadowSelf
- InitialConsciousnessLevel (float): 0.5
- bCanInteract (bool): true
- InteractionRange (float): 150.0
- AuraIntensity (float): 1.0

Events:
- BeginPlay:
  - Initialize NPC Behavior Component
  - Set up visual effects based on archetype
  - Configure dialogue system

- OnConsciousnessStateChanged:
  - Update visual effects
  - Change particle system parameters
  - Trigger appropriate animations

- OnTransformationTriggered:
  - Play transformation VFX
  - Update mesh materials
  - Trigger consciousness transition animation

- OnEmotionalResonance:
  - Adjust aura intensity
  - Update particle colors
  - Influence nearby environmental elements

Functions:
- InitializeArchetype(ENPCArchetype Archetype):
  - Set up archetype-specific properties
  - Configure behavior data table reference
  - Initialize visual representation

- UpdateVisualState():
  - Sync visuals with consciousness state
  - Update material parameters
  - Adjust lighting and effects

- HandlePlayerInteraction():
  - Check interaction conditions
  - Trigger appropriate dialogue
  - Respond based on player's consciousness level

Animation Blueprint: ABP_TranspersonalCharacter
Behavior Tree: BT_TranspersonalNPC
Blackboard: BB_TranspersonalNPC